 .../ui/trait-default-method-assoc-type.out    | 143 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../ui/trait-default-method-assoc-type.rs     |  12 ++
 3 files changed, 186 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 charon/tests/ui/trait-default-method-assoc-type.out
 create mode 100644 charon/tests/ui/trait-default-method-assoc-type.rs

